Instructions for running/testing program on Debian/Ubuntu distros

Install node.js:

  curl -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_6.x | sudo -E bash -
  sudo apt-get install -y nodejs

While in the project directory run 'npm install' to install dependencies

While in the project directory run 'npm start' to run program

Navigate to 'localhost:3000' to access the app for testing
